text:
The original video went down for some reason so I had to reupload it. It was the very first original song I uploaded back in 2007 and YouTube's sound quality was mono and pretty bad anyways.

But yeah this is the first song I made with FL Studio when I got it and it made me realise that I liked composing music. Super basic but special to me because of that.

The next VGM is still coming out tonight.
